name: stationery 001
description:
Set of 20 custom printed A2 (4.25 x 5.5") notecards on extra thick paper. Includes white envelope with printed return address.

Please include the name and return address to be printed in the personalization form on our checkout page.

If you would like a color other than the ones listed, a custom envelope color, or an envelope liner, please select "other" and let us know what you prefer in our "special instructions" box on the checkout page.

Once you place your order, Walnut Paperie will email a proof within 5 business days.
